                longDescription:
                  '<div><h1>Boys Graphic Tees</h1><p>Add some personality to his everyday look with boys graphic tees from The Children\'s Place. Check out our stylish spin on the traditional tee with our cool shirts for boys.</p><div class="read-more-target"><p>Comfy and casual, our boys t shirts are a "go-to" fave for boys of all ages. Shop all our short sleeve tees in cool graphics and fun statement designs. We\'ve got all the colors and styles kids want.</p><p>When it gets a little cooler, our boys long sleeve tees are always a hit. Pair them with just about anything including the latest denim fits, chino pants, joggers or activewear. The perfect pick for every day, our graphic tees are made of cool and breathable cotton... along with tagless labels for itch-free comfort he\'ll appreciate.</p><p>Get the whole family in on the graphic tee trend with matching daddy and mommy t-shirts. Shop family tees in all the must-have cool designs, along with the cutest matching graphic bodysuits for baby! We\'ve got everything from patriotic colorful Americana tees for summer to dad and kid matching shirts for the holidays.</p><p>Shopping our PLACE is better than ever! Download our <a href="https://www.childrensplace.com/us/content/mobile?icid=mbapp_glft_mbapplp_txt_070115_null">mobile app</a> and see the latest kids\' trends, check locations/hours, manage your <a href="https://www.childrensplace.com/us/content/myplace-rewards-page">My Place Rewards</a> account and more. Shopping online is easier than ever at The Children\'s Place.</p></div>',
