                longDescription:
                  '<div class="body-copy"> <h1>Boys Jeans</h1><p>When it comes to awesome pants style, it&rsquo;s in his jeans. Whether you need basic boys jeans for your casual kid or, something trendy for your fashionable tween, we&rsquo;ve got it at The Children&rsquo;s Place. From loose and bootcut, to straight and skinny, he&rsquo;ll get the look and feel he wants and you&rsquo;ll get it at a great price.</p><p>Choose from a variety of washes, from black to medium to deep blue, then pair them with a stylish polo, button-down shirt or graphic tee for a custom look. All of our jeans for boys come with plenty of comfort features that&rsquo;ll keep him happy throughout the day, including:</p><p>Pockets, pockets and more pockets. Every kid&rsquo;s jeans need extra pockets. Choose from five-pocket styling so he can store all his favorite things, like toys, lunch money and everything in between.</p><p>Inner adjustable button tabs. Is he picky about how his jeans fit? These inner-tabs let him adjust his jeans for a more customized feel.</p><p>Tagless labels. No one likes itchy labels, especially kids. This simple design feature creates a comfy wear, every time.</p><p>Is finding the perfect fit for him a challenge? At The Children&rsquo;s Place, you can use our <a href="/shop/us/content/size-chart">size chart</a> to find just the right fit for every child in the family, whether you&rsquo;re shopping for tops, bottoms, shoes, sleepwear or accessories. We even have <a href="/shop/us/search/boys-clothing/boys-special-sizes">extended sizes for boys</a>! Shop today and find the perfect boys clothing, as well as our entire collection of <a href="/shop/us/search/boys-clothing/boys-accessories">accessories</a>, <a href="/shop/us/search/childrens-shoes-kids-shoes/boys-shoes">shoes</a>, <a href="/shop/us/search/boys-clothing/boys-performance-active">performance active</a> wear and more at <a href="/shop/us/home">The Children&rsquo;s Place</a>.</p></div>',
